{"tid":2031022,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"★港區政協委員：強調香港的房屋問題是深層次問題","createTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T02:56:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"90c8e8b2aee521171afe9a1bdd83aea7cb23b0b7","tid":2031022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"港區政協委員黃國指：「強調國安法針對少數犯了破壞國家安全少數人，保護大多數香港人過正常安穩的生活，因為只有社會安穩，做生意營商環境才有保證，市民才可安居樂業過正常生活。」<br />\n<br />\n他亦引述韓正，談及香港民生問題。<br />\n<br />\n黃國稱：<strong>「他強調香港的房屋問題是深層次問題</strong>之一，希望香港恢復社會穩定後，集中精力解決香港的經濟、社會深層次矛盾，中央政府全力支持香港。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5ec8bbee335d19153ff47be7/%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5ec8bbee335d19153ff47be7%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A2%2583&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=c919316c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5ec8bbee335d19153ff47be7/%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%87%9F%E5%95%86%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83</a>"},{"pid":"cc49a8366d5888ff8060d6b8eadc303cbf3a6665","tid":2031022,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\